{"type": "article", "id": 11597, "title": "Candamill  2015 年秋季包袋", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-03T11:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061357480ZvMasSI2zcdb7ni.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t纽约潮牌 Candamill 最近推出了其 2015 年秋季包袋系列，颜色除了黑白灰以外，还有这一季最流行的酒红色，在材料上，意大利皮革和金属碰撞出了别样的质感。整个系列既有建筑物一样的严谨，也充满潮流和现代感，气质非常出众。这是<a href=\"http://www.candamill.com/\" target=\"_blank\">他们的官方主页</a>，可以查看购买信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135718Rid0KnjOxzGWpgeu.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"689\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.63796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135719QrfWJdXaRFN1O6Yp.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"613\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.02166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135719kX9vKfAgYxhPRzGl.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"835\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.39166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135720ymvgZF8VAj0Ji42o.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"743\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.23833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261357215f4XxDkKYmgHtcnE.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"899\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135721af7E3hMF4Agu5sTJ.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"721\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.20166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}